title: EPA: Mauritius to adhere to new provisions (Government of the Republic of Mauritius)
text: ( Source : Government of the Republic of Mauritius ) GIS - 16 October 2015 : Mauritius will sign the Joint Undertaking on Administrative Cooperation for the Implementation of the Cumulation Provisions contained in the Economic Partnership
